{"tid":1818263,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度前年平均15分鐘就有一名婦女被強姦","createTime":"2020-01-09T18:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T19:09:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a5524e60775707150fb0050e63070b5691dc3167","tid":1818263,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:17:14.000Z","msg":"印度政府數據顯示，2018年印度平均每15分鐘，就有一名婦女被強姦。<br />\n<br />\n內政部公布年度犯罪報告，指2018年接獲近34000宗婦女被強姦的報告，數字與2017年差不多，只有八成半人被檢控，當中更只有兩成七人被定罪。由於舉報強姦在部分地區被視為禁忌，以及姦殺案會被視作謀殺，估計實際涉及強姦的數字更高。<br />\n<br />\n有婦女組織認為，印度仍然是由男性統治，多數法官亦是男性，性侵犯婦女的罪行往往不被重視，警方在調查方面，亦缺乏敏感性。<br />\n<br />\n雖然印度政府早前成立快速審理法庭，並加大對涉及性罪行疑犯的刑罰，但有執政黨成員說，印度的法醫實驗室數目很少，快速審理法庭的法官亦不多，因此未能處理大量案件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501960-20200110.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501960-20200110.htm&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdC%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=a9ed1e4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501960-20200110.htm&h=512cc3d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501960-20200110.htm</a>"},{"pid":"df03c61d99dd661b8ab95025635cb7eda3970d0f","tid":1818263,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:18:08.000Z","msg":"印度不該是這樣的"},{"pid":"c0b29e3ce3452cd40af33a4e038582a5406c7c5c","tid":1818263,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:18:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"119000a9c4a642c6c3fd464561a2d90b1c16a0e6","tid":1818263,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:19:23.000Z","msg":"種性制度真係on9到爆<br />\n垃圾國家"},{"pid":"9a5c79037ded4e7beb021e4cf6855cb7c089f6ee","tid":1818263,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:21:12.000Z","msg":"見到標題啲字個人醒一醒 15分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77db40545deb957b13fa8a077e88691155c5acf","tid":1818263,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T19:09:09.000Z","msg":"如果香港每兩日就有一個人被強姦 咁算唔算強姦大國？"}]}